{"tid":1038803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【3屍命案】「皓仔」同班同學家長：兒子情緒受影響「好唔開心」","createTime":"2019-02-27T03:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T17:32:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"70cb4480bd9efe65c5a7a8b95869bf7b281e3bfa","tid":1038803,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:10:01.000Z","msg":"西營盤3屍命案，42歲姓羅男戶主、40歲姓陳妻子及7歲兒子「皓仔」喪命。其中慘死的「皓仔」，在薄扶林道香港潮商學校讀二年班。與「皓仔」就讀同一班的學生家長今晨表示，已接獲校方通告獲悉事件，她兒子是「皓仔」的好朋友，兒子知道「皓仔」去世，感到「好唔開心」，該名家長亦讚「皓仔」好乖。<br />\n曹女士的兒子與「皓仔」讀同一班，兒子與「皓仔」感情很好，「佢哋係好好的朋友，阿仔知道件事唔開心，發脾氣，我都識皓仔，佢好乖」。她說「皓仔」讀一年級時更是班長，經常參加學校的活動，「佢爸爸媽媽都會一齊參加，佢哋冇乜嘢，好好傾，我自己乜嘢活動都參加，次次都見到佢哋，一家三口感情好好。」她說昨日兒子返家後不開心，「好彩同佢傾吓、玩吓就冇乜嘢。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190227/large/1551234826_46d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190227%2Flarge%2F1551234826_46d9.jpg&h=adbb12b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曹女士讚「皓仔」好乖有禮貌。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190227/large/1551232922_7dff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190227%2Flarge%2F1551232922_7dff.jpg&h=019b33ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曹女士（圖左）的兒子與「皓仔」是同班同學，她說兒子獲悉事件後很不開心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190227/large/1551232922_4d01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190227%2Flarge%2F1551232922_4d01.jpg&h=c6d29798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「皓仔」在薄扶林道香港潮商學校讀二年班。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190227/59307890\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190227%2F59307890&d=zkxYWYOkbsQg7WdKzXEy6Xfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=cccccb4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190227%2F59307890&h=acf09d16\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190227/59307890</a>"},{"pid":"906a9289e9a922ebc4a6adc8f4131df76d2d2f8a","tid":1038803,"uid":136186,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:12:04.000Z","msg":"投錯胎<br />\n下世加油"},{"pid":"f28a6fcfdeab986e5a4f2301a5accc3cd872af97","tid":1038803,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"話佢搬左屋企咪得"},{"pid":"43aebcb6bef344c1d5ab3a3d9c28d76d219991d5","tid":1038803,"uid":37733,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"f28a6fcfdeab986e5a4f2301a5accc3cd872af97","tid":1038803,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"話佢搬左屋企咪得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"宜家7歲識得上連登自己睇啦<br />\n講大話呃到邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fbbfcb91293ab22ecd73790daa781f5f173b2d8","tid":1038803,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43aebcb6bef344c1d5ab3a3d9c28d76d219991d5","tid":1038803,"uid":37733,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"f28a6fcfdeab986e5a4f2301a5accc3cd872af97","tid":1038803,"uid":55597,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:15:26.000Z","msg":"話佢搬左屋企咪得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:30:53.000Z","msg":"宜家7歲識得上連登自己睇啦<br />\n講大話呃到邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有部手機就上到網查到"},{"pid":"6886f96fbdee241b9a48363eb0a78a92c65f889e","tid":1038803,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>話佢搬左屋企咪得</blockquote><br />\n搬左去天國"},{"pid":"4caf